<b>Howard William "Howie" Morenz</b>, (<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../819/15819.xml">
June 21</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../652/34652.xml">
1902</link> – <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../053/20053.xml">
